               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of Täklä Haymanot, መልክአ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡, Prayer of Mary at Bartos, Prayer to Mary, "Guard me", Hymn to Saint George, “O who is quick for help,” ኦ፡ ፍጡነ፡ ረድኤት፡, Image of Gabra Manfas Qǝddus, መልክአ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡, Prayer of the Covenant, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡, Anaphora of Our Lord Jesus Christ, Prayer, "For the sake of the peaceful, holy things", በእንተ፡ ቅድሳት፡ ሰላማዊት፡, Prayer after taking Communion, God of the Luminaries, እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘብርሃናት፡, Supplications, መስተብቍዕ, Absolution of the Father, Image of the Gate of Light, Image of the Praises of Mary, ውዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡</summary>
               </msContents>
